<tr id="L318"><td><a href="#L318">318</a></td><td>CLARK:  The decay rate of these Z-particles makes it almost impossible to trace the source.</td></tr>

<tr id="L319"><td><a href="#L319">319</a></td><td>LAFORGE:  I'm correlating particle trajectories. They're beginning to align. Wait a minute. I have coordinates thirty four degrees north, sixty two degrees east, at an altitude of two hundred ten kilometres.</td></tr>

