<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Athenaeum</td></tr>
<tr id="L322"><td><a href="#L322">322</a></td><td>PICARD:  Jared, you've described quite thoroughly the history of your people before and after Ardra's first visit. But I am a little unclear about the change itself. Did Ardra simply snap her fingers and transform the planet into this paradise?</td></tr>

<tr id="L323"><td><a href="#L323">323</a></td><td>JARED:  No, the changes occurred gradually over a long period of time.</td></tr>

<tr id="L324"><td><a href="#L324">324</a></td><td>PICARD:  Did she personally form the government that so peacefully ruled this planet for a millennium?</td></tr>

<tr id="L325"><td><a href="#L325">325</a></td><td>JARED:  No, historical records indicate a council was convened to assess our options. They drew up a new constitution which the population later ratified.</td></tr>

<tr id="L326"><td><a href="#L326">326</a></td><td>PICARD:  I see. So she advised this council?</td></tr>

<tr id="L327"><td><a href="#L327">327</a></td><td>JARED:  No.</td></tr>

<tr id="L328"><td><a href="#L328">328</a></td><td>PICARD:  No? Then she must have destroyed all the weapons on the planet.</td></tr>

<tr id="L329"><td><a href="#L329">329</a></td><td>JARED:  No, our leaders did that. And they signed a treaty of non-aggression.</td></tr>

<tr id="L330"><td><a href="#L330">330</a></td><td>PICARD:  Well then, let's move on to the environmental gains on Ventax Two. How were those accomplished</td></tr>

<tr id="L331"><td><a href="#L331">331</a></td><td>JARED:  We shifted our economy from an industrial to an agrarian base. It was more ecologically sound.</td></tr>

<tr id="L332"><td><a href="#L332">332</a></td><td>PICARD:  But Ardra must have purified the polluted water and air?</td></tr>

<tr id="L333"><td><a href="#L333">333</a></td><td>JARED:  No, the record shows there were a series of initiatives covering everything from atmospheric contaminants to waste disposal.</td></tr>

<tr id="L334"><td><a href="#L334">334</a></td><td>PICARD:  Did she not even pick up one piece of trash?</td></tr>

<tr id="L335"><td><a href="#L335">335</a></td><td>JARED:  Ardra had left Ventax Two before the environmental reforms began.</td></tr>

<tr id="L336"><td><a href="#L336">336</a></td><td>PICARD:  Forgive me, but it sounds as if with a great deal of hard work and courage, your ancestors changed this world all by themselves.</td></tr>

<tr id="L337"><td><a href="#L337">337</a></td><td>ARDRA:  Objection. The advocate is drawing conclusions.</td></tr>

<tr id="L338"><td><a href="#L338">338</a></td><td>DATA:  Sustained. I will draw my own conclusions, if you do not mind. Sir.</td></tr>

<tr id="L339"><td><a href="#L339">339</a></td><td>PICARD:  No further questions.</td></tr>

